items.heading: What is prolific cloud?
items.text: Prolific Cloud is a solution to build, innovate, and create professional websites for personal and business needs, requiring no background or knowledge of programming or coding.

items.heading: Are there any recurring fees, or is it a one-time payment for the service?
items.text: Prolific Cloud aims to inspire a generation of entrepreneurs to build their websites. Although Prolific Cloud follows a subscription-based model, the aim is to motivate all levels of thinkers and innovators to create an online presence. Hence, the recurring monthly fees are one of the lowest in the industry, and additional discounts on annual payments. There are no hidden costs.

items.heading: Are the pre-built websites customizable?
items.text: Prolific Cloud provides its users with hundreds of free templates that users can import instantly. The imported contents are customizable. Users can design additional content to the template or remove an existing section, column or components. The Page Builder drag-and-drop building tools make designing extremely easy to use, even for novices with no tech background.

items.heading: Why should I choose Prolific Cloud
items.text: Prolific Cloud is determined to empower non-programmers and non-coders with the tools and means to design and publish personal and business websites. In addition, the eCommerce features enable you to stretch your business limit by reaching more users with a reliable website and payment system from anywhere in the world. There is a 24/7 support staff ready to assist you with your website's extra requirements. Prolific Cloud is perfect for new entrepreneurs, small businesses for its easy-to-manage dashboard. Sign Up for a 30-day free trial to enjoy all the premium and flagship features without entering payment details.

items.heading: Where can I get support?
items.text: To assist users with the website administration, the Prolific Cloud team regularly releases tutorial videos, blogs design guides, tips, and user guides. A dedicated group of experts is always available to take messages and queries from the user on any social media platform or email. Get updates on our Linkedin and Facebook pages. Follow us on YouTube and watch all the videos to know more about the Page Builder.
